===Noun===
'''Christmas ham'''

#(''countable and uncountable'') A [[ham]], [[boiled]] and then [[baked]] in oven with [[mustard]], served [[sliced]] at [[Christmas]] as one of the traditionally most important parts of the [[Scandinavian]] ''[[julbord]]'' (special Christmas time ''[[smörgåsbord]]'')


